********************************************************
* Make sure you've enough shared memory, the xine FAQ  *
* advises to have the following sysctl settings:       *
*                                                      *
* kern.ipc.shmmax=67108864                             *
* kern.ipc.shmall=32768                                *
*                                                      *
* To suppress many xitk warnings, please put following *
* setting in ~/.xitkrc.                                *
*                                                      *
* feature.shm = 0                                      *
********************************************************
